text: Trude Möhwaldová (born 25 March 1915, date of death unknown) was a Czech alpine skier. She competed in the women's combined event at the 1936 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1915 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Czech female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Czechoslovakia Category:Alpine skiers at the 1936 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
